{"tid":1626600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BB都知對家轉L左玩法","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T22:10:07.000Z","uid":258522,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b2b40d49353011e393f1cd0e554ae3dc7a7009","tid":1626600,"uid":258522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:02:05.000Z","msg":"立完蒙面法後，預期既開大片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無出現到<br />\n呢兩日接近無暴力清場，元朗果單開槍我會classify 為休班狗忽上腦，只係一個渣槍藍絲，而不是一個清場鎮壓既指令或者方針。<br />\n<br />\n相比起929, 101。果種叫做靠「嚇」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，諗住嚇L到你地班仆街唔L出黎。而家個方針，好似想轉做「屈」。唔開所有商場，港鐵，同埋大量既破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，影響大量市民，對家係想有民意既逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話我係分化L，或者想割住。大量既破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我個人係十分心涼，都唔反對去咁做，因體制上我地尋求唔到方法解決，激進行為係其中一個出路，警暴，警察偏頗既執法，都使我地激進行為既正當性增加。<br />\n但，對家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">轉左玩法</span></span></strong>係客觀既事實，我地要<span style=\"color: blue;\">[size=5]Be Water[/size=6]</span> 應對。呢兩日警暴，比起 929，101 差幾L遠。開始減少警暴，想洗白黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同話示威者搞到香港變死城。<br />\n<br />\n我才疏學淺，只希望往後既日子，大家都可以做得更好，如果我地唔盡我地所能做到最好，係對唔住之前手足既犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。以下我有幾點建議：<br />\n<br />\n1. 警暴減少左，和理非更加要出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。因安全左，更加係呢一刻唔可以割，全部人蒙面，至少帶mask 。如果你話怕坐一年，或者怕罰$25000, 我會以你為恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再講，個個咁做，佢拉得哂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n2. 文宣係好重要，或者好似對家D whatapp 流言咁，一定要一傳十，十傳百<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。香港變死城，責任都不止在示威者，在政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，事前咩都未發生就關港鐵，商場，咁關人忍事咩。<br />\n<br />\n3. 一講開破壞事件，一定要話係卧底警渣，或者係大陸特務做。如果有警渣扮示威者既相，用文宣煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，要將變死城責任掉番比政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n4. 不必叫停破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，都不必捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因現實上做唔到。但之前有個守則，我覺得係要守番，有無人可以repost<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩好諗法，我會再加上去，同意請推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e3b07da724db9928aac714b2aedc49cc6cc202b9","tid":1626600,"uid":258522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffdf8b7d100774326d31250a388b3d72af1bfcae","tid":1626600,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"睇路"},{"pid":"fa6f5c1c8a60729ec870fd6681d128dcf4990b55","tid":1626600,"uid":67454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"而家暫時適合和理非，大家都試探緊對方下一步想點"},{"pid":"3087f0945221495e8cb2fc3be1b2fe7ee54304a4","tid":1626600,"uid":258522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f251340ae64c010dbe6d26728e6af19ccaff64c1","tid":1626600,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"94ff49003822826b1a86b236ada2eb09b7cb0a18","tid":1626600,"uid":62236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"如果此刻不站在此..."},{"pid":"0c34931495f4b7a6b2b77c17c8423426625c20bd","tid":1626600,"uid":258522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96a2ee215065a7cb6